    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped to Gradation 1 and satisfied by documented procedural controls consistent with MRL 2 expectations. Validation evidence demonstrates CFD model predicts RHI within 15 % of experimental measurements across the full operating envelope. The model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Decision consequence is High; however, the Medium model influence and satisfactory validation evidence support an Accepted determination at MRL 2.",
